{%- set employee = frappe.get_doc("Employee", doc.employee) -%}

{% set current_date = frappe.utils.nowdate() %}
{% set formatted_current_date = frappe.utils.get_datetime(current_date).strftime("%B %e, %Y") %}

{% set formatted_date = frappe.utils.get_datetime(doc.transfer_date).strftime("%B %e, %Y") %}

<div>


{{ formatted_current_date or '' }}
<br><br>

<h3 align='center'>Transfer Letter</h3><br><br>
<p>{{ doc.employee_name or '' }}</p><br>
<p style='width:230px;'>{{ employee.current_address or '' }}</p><br><br>


Dear {{ doc.employee_name or '' }},
<br><br>
<p style='text-align:justify'>In accordance with the management decision, it has been decided to relocate your services to our 
<b>{%- for row in doc.transfer_details -%}
        {%- if "Department" in row.property -%}
            {{ row.new or '' }}
        {%- endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}
</b> at 
<b>{%- for row in doc.transfer_details -%}
        {%- if "Branch" in row.property -%}
            {{ row.new or '' }}
        {%- endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}
</b> 
with effect from <b>{{ formatted_date or '' }}</b>. You will report to 
<b>Future: &nbsp;{%- for row in doc.transfer_details -%}
        {%- if "Reports to" in row.property -%}
            {%- set reports_to_name = frappe.get_doc("Employee", row.new) -%}
            {{ row.new or '' }}: {{ reports_to_name.employee_name or '' }}, {{ reports_to_name.designation or '' }}
        {%- endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}</b>.
<br><br>
You are advised to please report at 
<b>{%- for row in doc.transfer_details -%}
        {%- if "Department" in row.property -%}
            {{ row.new or '' }}
        {%- endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}
</b> - 
<b>{%- for row in doc.transfer_details -%}
        {%- if "Branch" in row.property -%}
            {{ row.new or '' }}
        {%- endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}
</b> 

on <b>{{ formatted_date or '' }}</b> at the start of the office hours. After handing over charge and obtaining release from 
<b>Current: &nbsp;{%- for row in doc.transfer_details -%}
        {%- if "Reports to" in row.property -%}
            {%- set reports_to_name = frappe.get_doc("Employee", row.current) -%}
            {{ row.current or '' }}: {{ reports_to_name.employee_name or '' }}, {{ reports_to_name.designation or '' }}
        {%- endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}</b>.
.<br><br>
Please familiarise yourself with the standing orders, attendance rules, outdoor duty procedures, Leave formalities and such other rules and regulations governing at the location.<br><br>
All other terms and conditions of your appointment letter remains unchanged.<br><br>
We wish you all the best and look forward to receive your continued efforts and application. <br><br>
Thanking you,<br><br></p>

<b>Yours faithfully,<br>
For {{ doc.company }}</b>


<br><br><br><br>

<b>{{ doc.employee_name or '' }}<br>{{ employee.designation or '' }}</b>
</div>

<div style="width: 100%; margin-top: 40px; position: relative;">
    <div style="position: absolute; left: 0;">
        <span></span>
    </div>
    <div style="position: absolute; right: 0;">
        <span style="border-top: 1px solid;"><b>I accept the above</b></span>
    </div>
</div>

